ng is a widely recognized Chinese actress. Often dubbed a “nepo baby,” Guan was born into an artistic family—her father, Guan Shaozeng, is a well-known actor, which gave her early access to the entertainment industry. This lineage, helped her rise swiftly through the ranks.\n\nStarting her career as a child star, Guan has built a prolific body of work spanning drama, romance, historical epics, and fantasy.","name":"Guan Xiaotong","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　关晓彤，演员、歌手，毕业于北京电影学院表演系本科班。童星出身的她被誉为“国民闺女”。\n\n　　2001年，完成个人出道作品《烟海沉浮》。2005年，凭借奇幻动作片《无极》被观众认识 。2008年，因在年代爱情剧《幸福还有多远》中饰演大丫而崭露头角。2014年，凭借时尚情感剧《一仆二主 》获国剧盛典观众喜爱的新人女演员奖。2015年，发行个人音乐专辑《十八》。\n\n　　2016年，因主演都市爱情剧《好先生》而获得广泛关注，并凭借该剧获得第23届上海电视节白玉兰奖最佳女配角奖；同年，与郑爽、周冬雨和杨紫共同被评为“90后四小花旦” 。2017年，主演的青春校园励志剧《极光之恋》播出。2018年7月23日，主演的青春热血格斗剧《甜蜜暴击》播出 。2019年1月4日，关晓彤为中国电影频道评选的演技派新生代四小花旦（另有张子枫、文淇和张雪迎）之一。","name":"关晓彤","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Quan Hiểu Đồng là nữ diễn viên, người mẫu, ca sĩ, MC người Trung Quốc thuộc dòng họ Qua Nhĩ Giai thị, dân tộc Mãn Châu. Cô bắt đầu đóng phim từ năm 4 tuổi, đã tham gia hơn 100 tác phẩm điện ảnh và truyền hình.","name":"Quan Hiểu Đồng","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"關曉彤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Гуань Сяо Тун","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"關曉彤，演員、歌手，畢業於北京電影學院表演系本科班。童星出身的她被譽為“國民閨女”。\n\n2001 年，完成個人出道作品《煙海沉浮》。2005 年，憑藉奇幻動作片《無極》被觀眾認識 。2008 年，因在年代愛情劇《幸福還有多遠》中飾演大丫而嶄露頭角。2014 年，憑藉時尚情感劇《一僕二主 》獲國劇盛典觀眾喜愛的新人女演員獎。2015 年，發行個人音樂專輯《十八》。\n\n2016 年，因主演都市愛情劇《好先生》而獲得廣泛關注，並憑藉該劇獲得第 23 屆上海電視節白玉蘭獎最佳女配角獎；同年，與鄭爽、周冬雨和楊紫共同被評為“90 後四小花旦” 。2017 年，主演的青春校園勵志劇《極光之戀》播出。2018 年 7 月 23 日，主演的青春熱血格鬥劇《甜蜜暴擊》播出 。2019 年 1 月 4 日，關曉彤為中國電影頻道評選的演技派新生代四小花旦（另有張子楓、文淇和張雪迎）之一。","name":"關曉彤","primary":false}}]}},"person_3042038_translations":{"at":1772689444772,"data":{"id":3042038,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Alix Villaret","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿利克斯·维拉雷特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"알릭스 빌라레","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿利克斯·維拉雷特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Аликс Вилларе","primary":false}}]}},"tv_227477_credits":{"at":1772689457429,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3436409,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"陆双","original_name":"陆双","popularity":0.2341,"profile_path":null,"character":"配音 (voice)","credit_id":"6757314e997d956422f46889","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2968424,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Qing Zu","original_name":"祖晴","popularity":0.7081,"profile_path":null,"character":"配音 (voice)","credit_id":"6757315a98c33892a2559ef5","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1908013,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Tuan Li","original_name":"李团","popularity":0.5718,"profile_path":null,"character":"配音 (voice)","credit_id":"67573176997d956422f468a0","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":4019686,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Yechuan Zhang","original_name":"Yechuan Zhang","popularity":0.6021,"profile_path":"/pFDkhoCGnHMRlXHbufVq5OKvMvH.jpg","character":"配音 (voice)","credit_id":"675731889bc20eaa4968121e","order":3}],"crew":[],"id":227477}},"person_1591398_translations":{"at":1772689458730,"data":{"id":1591398,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Cornelio Sunny is an Indonesian actor.  His father is from a Mexican descent, while his mother is from Palembang.","name":"Cornelio Sunny","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia","english_name":"Indonesian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Cornelio Sunny","primary":true}}]}},"person_1334638_translations":{"at":1772689460418,"data":{"id":1334638,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jack Andrew Lowden (born June 2, 1990) is a Scottish actor. Following a four-year stage career, his first major international onscreen success was in the 2016 BBC miniseries War & Peace, which led to starring roles in feature films. Starring as River Cartwright in the Apple TV series Slow Horses since 2020, he has received nominations for a Primetime Emmy Award and a Golden Globe Award. \n\nLowden starred as Eric Liddell in the 2012 play Chariots of Fire in London. In 2014, he won an Olivier Award and the Ian Charleson Award for his role as Oswald in Richard Eyre's 2013 adaptation of Ibsen's Ghosts. \n\nIn 2013, he began to take on substantial roles in British television series and feature films, including The Tunnel (2013) and '71 (2014). He also had leading roles in the BBC miniseries The Passing Bells (2014) and War & Peace (2016). Other screen roles include the title role as golfing legend Tommy Morris in Tommy's Honour (2016); the starring role of Morrissey in the biopic England Is Mine (2017); a main-cast role as an RAF fighter-pilot in Christopher Nolan's Dunkirk (2017); a starring role in the Scottish Highlands thriller Calibre (2018, for which he won the British Academy Scotland Award for Best Film Actor); Lord Darnley in Mary Queen of Scots (2018); a starring role as a plantation owner in 19th-century Jamaica in the 2018 BBC miniseries The Long Song; and as Zak \"Zodiac\" Bevis in the 2019 comedy-drama WWE film Fighting with My Family.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Jack Lowden, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Jack Lowden","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Jack Lowden (* 2. Juni 1990 in Chelmsford, Essex) ist ein britischer Schauspieler.  Ab dem Jahr 2010 übernahm er kleinere Rollen in Fernseh- und Filmproduktionen. In der Filmbiografie England Is Mine, die beim Edinburgh International Film Festival 2017 Premiere feierte und am 4. August 2017 in die Kinos kam, übernahm er die Hauptrolle von Steven Patrick Morrissey. In Christopher Nolans Kriegsfilm Dunkirk aus dem gleichen Jahr ist Lowden ebenfalls in einer Hauptrolle zu sehen.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"잭 로던","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"傑克·洛登","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"杰克·劳登（Jack Lowden），1990年6月2日出生于英格兰埃塞克斯，演员。\n\n2010年，出演个人首部电视剧《Being Victor》，从而进入演艺圈。2014年，凭借舞台剧《群鬼》获得劳伦斯·奥立佛奖最佳男配角奖。2017年，凭借剧情片《敦刻尔克》获得更多关注。2018年，由其出演的剧情片《玛丽女王》上映。2019年，在传记片《为家而战》中饰演扎克。2024年，凭借主演的谍战剧《流人第三季》获得第76届黄金时段艾美奖剧情类最佳男配角奖提名。2025年5月23日，主演的电影《龙卷风》英国上映。","name":"杰克·劳登","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"جک لودن","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"傑克·勞登（傑克·洛登），1990 年 6 月 2 日出生於英格蘭埃塞克斯，演員。\n\n2010 年，出演個人首部電視劇《Being Victor》，從而進入演藝圈。2014 年，憑借舞台劇《群鬼》獲得勞倫斯·奧立佛獎最佳男配角獎。2017 年，憑借劇情片《敦刻爾克》獲得更多關注。2018 年，由其出演的劇情片《蘇格蘭女王：爭名奪後》上映。2019 年，在傳記片《我的勁揪家族》中飾演紮克。2024 年，憑借主演的諜戰劇《流人第三季》獲得第 76 屆黃金時段艾美獎劇情類最佳男配角獎提名。2025 年 5 月 23 日，主演的電影《龍卷風》英國上映。","name":"傑克·洛登","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джек Лауден","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джек Лоуден","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ջեք Լաուդեն","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джэк Лаўдэн","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"جاك لودين","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Τζακ Λόουντεν","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジャック・ロウデン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"ג'ק לאודן","primary":false}}]}},"movie_9552_keywords":{"at":1772689461126,"data":{"id":9552,"keywords":[{"id":521,"name":"washington dc, usa"},{"id":3684,"name":"religion and supernatural"},{"id":2626,"name":"exorcism"},{"id":3649,"name":"holy water"},{"id":11627,"name":"paranormal phenomena"},{"id":9712,"name":"possession"},{"id":5569,"name":"vomit"},{"id":10138,"name":"satan"},{"id":10093,"name":"priest"},{"id":10112,"name":"ouija board"},{"id":15001,"name":"demon"},{"id":18402,"name":"strong language"},{"id":157008,"name":"roman catholic church"},{"id":157701,"name":"psychotic"},{"id":161261,"name":"demo